---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="attributions - leshy" description="credits for open-source tools and free resources used on this site" bodyClass="post-page">

  <nav class="post-nav">
    <a href="/">&larr; home</a>
  </nav>

  <header class="post-header">
    <h1>attributions</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="prose">
    <p>this site is built with open-source tools and uses free resources from generous creators. thank you to everyone below.</p>

    <h2>frameworks & libraries</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Astro</a> &mdash; static site framework</li>
      <li><a href="https://react.dev/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">React</a> &mdash; UI components</li>
      <li><a href="https://supabase.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Supabase</a> &mdash; authentication &amp; database</li>
      <li><a href="https://tonejs.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tone.js</a> &mdash; audio synthesis &amp; sampling</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/ianprime0509/pitchy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">pitchy</a> &mdash; pitch detection for the tuner</li>
      <li><a href="https://recharts.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Recharts</a> &mdash; charts for progress tracking</li>
      <li><a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/web-analytics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare Web Analytics</a> &mdash; privacy-friendly analytics</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>audio samples</h2>

    <h3>metronome</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://freesound.org/people/Sadiquecat/sounds/793346/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Metronome click</a> by Sadiquecat &mdash; CC0</li>
      <li><a href="https://freesound.org/people/Druminfected/sounds/250552/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Metronome.wav</a> by Druminfected &mdash; CC0</li>
      <li><a href="https://freesound.org/people/m1rk0/sounds/50071/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">metronom_pling.wav</a> by m1rk0 (Mirko Horstmann) &mdash; <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CC BY 3.0</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://freesound.org/people/unfa/sounds/243748/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Metronome 2kHz (strong pulse)</a> by unfa &mdash; CC0</li>
      <li><a href="https://freesound.org/people/lennartgreen/sounds/566888/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Click Metronome atonal high</a> by lennartgreen &mdash; CC0</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>instruments</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://sfzinstruments.github.io/pianos/salamander/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Salamander Grand Piano</a> by Alexander Holm &mdash; CC BY 3.0</li>
      <li><a href="https://freepats.zenvoid.org/Guitar/acoustic-guitar.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">FreePats Acoustic Guitar</a> &mdash; CC0</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>hosting & services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://pages.github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Pages</a> &mdash; static site hosting</li>
      <li><a href="https://freesound.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Freesound</a> &mdash; collaborative sound library</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <a href="/">home</a>
  </footer>

</Base>
